trans-unit.source: Determines the serialization method used for a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 에 사용 되는 serialization 메서드를 결정 한 <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings.SerializeAs%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> object controls the serialization mode for a single profile property setting.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings.SerializeAs%2A>의 속성은 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings>개체를 단일 프로필 속성 설정에 대 한 serialization 모드를 제어 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings.SerializeAs%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object is serialized using binary serialization.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> 이진 직렬화를 사용 하 여 serialize 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The provider has implicit knowledge of the type and is responsible for deciding how to serialize the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object into the data store.
trans-unit.target: 공급자 유형으로 암시적 알지가 책임 serialize 하는 방법을 결정 하는 데는 <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> 개체를 데이터 저장소에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object is serialized to a simple string.
The profile <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> is serialized as XML using XML serialization.
trans-unit.target: 프로필 <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> XML 직렬화를 사용 하 여 XML로 serialize 됩니다.
